window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Auroraâ€™s greatest entrepreneur has been murdered, and only the truth will save Alchemist Ortez from the gallows.</b></p> <p>Facing a heated courtroom of strangers, he must now recall the events that brought him here as a fellow alchemist probes his memory. Such is the job of alchemists: administering elixirs in order to see into the minds of men. Their dreams. Their nightmares. Their secrets.</p> <p>But while everyone believes him guilty, Alchemist Ortez knows what they do not.</p> <p>He was hired by the victim for a job unlike any they could imagine. They would never guess what other mysteries lie buried beneath the mountain metropolis of Aurora, a cave-enclosed city where countless gas lamps illuminate the endless night.</p> <p><i>Trial of the Alchemist </i>is a gaslamp mystery ripe with twists, adventure, and romance.</p>"; 
